'''Laurence Doherty''' is an actor. In ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]'' he is portraying a [[Great Master 3|Great Master]] in [[Meereen]].

Doherty wasn't credited for his appearance in "Breaker of Chains", but twitted an screencap of a scene of the episode in which he appears among several [[Great Masters]].<ref>[https://twitter.com/DocFourFour/status/458379621978107905/photo/1/large Laurence Doherty's twit]</ref>
